  parcel=>{
  -Dev build
  - Local server
  -hot module replacement(hmr) -automaticlly refresh page when save code
  --caching --faster builds
  - Bundling
  - compressing
  -image optimization
  -consistent hashing
  -code splitting
  - differential bundling - support older browsers
  - Dignostic
  -Error handling
  -HTTPs
  -tree shaking-- removes unused code
  -different dev and prod bundles


  }
